# agent_email

Standalone scaffold for Stage 19 extraction of email operations.

This package currently provides:
- inbound/outbound/loop control contracts
- read/report control contract (`report`)
- runner scaffold with safe write-local default behavior
- sqlite parity adapter scaffold for email queue/state counters
